  "chunk_type": "subsection",
  "content": "Prerequisites: Divine rank 6, Dex 29.\nBenefit: As a move action, the deity can travel up to 30 feet per divine rank, as though using the dimension door spell, except that the deity never appears within a solid object and can act immediately after teleporting.\nSuggested Portfolio Elements: Travel.",
